text: Virginie Delvingt (born 8 July 1971) is a French badminton player. She competed in women's singles and women's doubles at the 1992 Summer Olympics in Barcelona. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:French female badminton players Category:Olympic badminton players of France Category:Badminton players at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Strasbourg
